{"tid":1917150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴推跌《有線》記者 警：現場人多混亂 有線：不接受解釋 警迴避事實 極度遺憾","createTime":"2020-03-09T10:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T16:27:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"121429f2225c253e4ee3d3203b54407d056f002e","tid":1917150,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T10:17:00.000Z","msg":"昨日（3月8日）是科大學生周梓樂逝世四個月，數百市民在將軍澳悼念，多人被捕。有防暴警員昨日用盾牌從後推撞《有線》記者，該記者頭部落地感到暈眩及耳鳴。<br />\n<br />\n警方回應《立場新聞》查詢時稱現場人多混亂，對記者受傷表示慰問，但強調記者要聽從警員指示保持適當距離。《有線新聞》則表明不接受警方解釋，要求警方盡快主動調查事件，交代涉事警員身分，又批評警方迴避具體事實，只作一般性回覆，極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E6%8E%A8%E8%B7%8C-%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%9A%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E8%BF%B4%E9%81%BF%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%A5%B5%E5%BA%A6%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BF%25B4%25E9%2581%25BF%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%2586%25BE%2F&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=4a37ef1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25B7%25B7%25E4%25BA%2582-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%2